== SAIL/OTrunk DIY

The DIY is a Rails applicaion for authoring and running SAIL/OTrunk activities.

The Trac instance for he DIY is located here: http://trac.cosmos.concord.org/diy/

== TESTING ==

right now, all tests live in spec/

and testing is done like so:
spec -fh spec > reports/spec.html

